\"color: orange;\">行動：</span><br />\n由教徒帶領為香港人權及民主祈禱<br />\n提交巨式請願信，並供在場人士簽署<br />\n喊叫英文號，包括撐法案訴求<br />\n&quot;Free Hong Kong, Pass the act.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動為和理非，不容許有任何衝擊行為</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">時間表：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skc24zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkc24zk.png&h=3cadacbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2xyrND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2xyrND.png&h=1b101412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12：30 遮打花園祈禱集會，評估人數<br />\n13：30 不經禮賓府，沿金鍾道紅棉路方向前往美領<br />\n13：50 經過花園道聖若瑟堂，唱聖歌及祈禱<br />\n14：00 美國領事館祈禱集會 <br />\n(如人數太多，以流水式在美領對出繞圈集會)<br />\n15：30  提交巨式請願信 / 請願信<br />\n17：00  離開禮賓府及美領相關範圍 (<span style=\"color: red;\">和平散去</span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">目前要做：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n1. 一人一信向美領通知集會+表達訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n電話: (852) 2523-9011<br />\n電子郵件: information_resource_center_hk@yahoo.com<br />\n電子郵件: HKPressTeam@state.gov<br />\n<br />\n範本：<br />\nDear sir or madam,<br />\n<br />\nAccording to the information from the web and social platform, there will be a peaceful assembly outside your office (Consulate General of the US) at Hong Kong time 14:00 on 8th September,2016 (this Sunday) in which a petition for the urge of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act will be expressed and a letter is hoped to be passed to your officer.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, I am writing to hopefully notify you for the event and ask that if there will be special arrangement such as assigning a officer to receive the letter on that day? It would be appreciated.<br />\n<br />\nI am also a supporter of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act. And I hope the voice of the Hong Kong people can be delivered to the US and related department.Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\n(你的名字)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>2. 需要有英文好巴寫請願信</strong></span><br />\n正常SIZE 及 巨型請願信各一封<br />\n巨型請願信內文較簡單，供集會人士簽署<br />\n如冇職員接信，正常SIZE星期一遞交<br />\n巨型請願信則放在美領門口，如圖<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgfFmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgfFmt.jpg&h=2f5218bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>3. 打印當日文宣及道具(如美國旗)</strong></span><br />\n建議一人一國旗，下面可打印：<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9UdrvE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9UdrvE.png&h=c7454fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7aj6wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7aj6wD.png&h=b55903f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrCiDc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrCiDc6.png&h=68b4225c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOLoPk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOLoPk2.png&h=27b41922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>4. 入TG討論公海</strong></span><br />\n入TG討論詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=f1c043ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ</a></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"541602402c9d7065402ce97a9e3644e77415f53d","tid":1535242,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"亦唔好高估中共可以稱霸世界嘅能力，"},{"pid":"2f0e9d9f31f56a870d910520548eeb9e164ca771","tid":1535242,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:38:49.000Z","msg":"因為點都唔會夠你鬥"},{"pid":"5dd577e90b98256413ec6039047f9bc27d2a4789","tid":1535242,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"又點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0a340903fc75b7a97e5eabc188e8c1f4143267","tid":1535242,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"佢驚中国唔撚死"},{"pid":"6300ae0464dff36af5752a5c06d7623eb15c8026","tid":1535242,"uid":284100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"又玻璃心"},{"pid":"90b5b813dc16af7218b2a5d6af6770486aa7dd01","tid":1535242,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"ご署名をお願いします！<br />\n香港における政府当局による強権的な動きをけん制するため、日本版『香港人権・民主主義法案』の議論を開始することを日本の国会議員に求めます。<br />\nPlease submit your signature!<br />\nWe are asking Japanese parliamentarians to start discussions on the Japanese version of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FrqWFBmbSp4&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=2c9fed77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4</a> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手簽同share. Thank you."},{"pid":"a0de90e24b6ce7f3759bafc9b0ce3551b0ef867f","tid":1535242,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"人地美國波蘭簽咩關你撚事呀？"},{"pid":"7c01e413df1dac0cee14fad24613907ef4833d43","tid":1535242,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4ef83e39aaf2acb0dcf9a564ac750701e1203c","tid":1535242,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"美國和波蘭近日簽署所謂的「5G安全聲明「，強調將嚴格控制5G網路設備供應商。中國外交部發言人耿爽在今天（3日）的外交部例行記者會上表示，美方對別國的5G網路建設指手畫腳，強拉甚至威脅其他國家要採取與美方一致的立場，這種單邊主義和霸權主義的行徑暴露無遺。奉勸美方不要高估自己的造謠能力，也不要低估別人的判斷能力。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人 耿爽：一段時間以來，美方在拿不出任何證據的情況下，泛化「國家安全」概念，濫用國家力量，無端打壓中國企業，這種行為既不光采，也不道德。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽強調，中方敦促美方停止泛化「國家安全」概念的錯誤做法，停止對中國的蓄意抹黑和指責，停止對中國企業的無理打壓。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人 耿爽：美方打壓中國企業，污衊中國的真實意圖是什麼？相信任何秉持公正、客觀立場的國家，都對此看得清清楚楚、明明白白。我們奉勸美方不要高估自己的造謠能力，也不要低估別人的判斷能力。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190903/32542686.html</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"咩拿不出任何證據？證據去到巴基斯坦都有喎！"},{"pid":"84a27792f4312ecc059291ef62f813e2342b9e73","tid":1535242,"uid":243967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"知啦知啦，知你造謠最叻，唔同你爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7db7b91d5aa4e735b36dc9580c2bfde9c48a4d","tid":1535242,"uid":194609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1abf5b3aa78a259e758ed304554c3f508fb122c5","tid":1535242,"uid":18948,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"講造謠點夠世界最大騙子集團嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外交部：不要高估自己的造謠能力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外交部不要高估自己的造謠能力"},{"pid":"42a1797d528223a1fafb5fbe86908c347b51ad17","tid":1535242,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"你口交部含撚含足咁多年都改變唔到世界對你既睇法<br />\n呢句你自己自含吞撚返佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104758c6ccfb253f2a0741e499413259b2c9a916","tid":1535242,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842be980ec36d67a3efb227dac00063cb668fa07","tid":1535242,"uid":274849,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"中國講大話真係好純熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大話經十四憶人講就變真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"波蘭，使唔使我地幫佢宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"